Currency Tracker

Instructions

TO run the application do,


bundle install
rake db:create
rake db:migrate

Signup to application, which will create the countries, currencies to that user,(getting currerncy & country data using savon gem, i.e. from http://www.webservicex.net/country.asmx?WSDL as like it was in github project, Looks sometimes http://www.webservicex.net/country.asmx?WSDL is down due to heavy traffic which may fail user signup process, if this happens please try again to sign up )



